{"tid":1300113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯27周年會慶聚餐　蔣麗芸：「要嚟就要比錢　唔好白食！」","createTime":"2019-07-09T09:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T10:09:08.000Z","uid":14328,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"14d72996e8f32fa701ca9ad73573ea71283f2f67","tid":1300113,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:14:01.000Z","msg":"民建聯27周年會慶聚餐，民建聯九龍西立法會議員蔣麗芸受訪時回應指稱，網民要買門票才能入內，又指如果他們想來可以購票，「不可以白食」。<br />\n<br />\n本港第一大政黨民建聯向來財力雄厚。《立場新聞》早前報道，民建聯最新一份在公司註冊處提交的財務報表，發現該黨的 2017/ 18年度（2017年4月至2018年3月底）的財政年度，民建聯錄得總收入1.25億元，創逾十年來非立法會或區議會換屆選舉年新高。<br />\n<br />\n對比該黨十前年、2008/09 年度（當年是立法會換屆選舉年）的總收入6218萬元，民建聯年度總收入在十年間翻倍。累計過去十個財政年度，民建聯共吸金近9.6億元。"},{"pid":"24e313afaccd20efd4325ca8a1b5023bae996dbd","tid":1300113,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"人之將死"},{"pid":"8f30e10851974224e9b997fe3877a1142e7cc1fc","tid":1300113,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0169f66fd8cfb80402e14bc6b29d527e1b50baaa","tid":1300113,"uid":216800,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"24e313afaccd20efd4325ca8a1b5023bae996dbd","tid":1300113,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"人之將死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:16:33.000Z","msg":"其言也柒"},{"pid":"f3fd2da1bd1849fee435a309c2dcde6542eb9234","tid":1300113,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0169f66fd8cfb80402e14bc6b29d527e1b50baaa","tid":1300113,"uid":216800,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"24e313afaccd20efd4325ca8a1b5023bae996dbd","tid":1300113,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"人之將死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:16:33.000Z","msg":"其言也柒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets